title: CRED REA Fish Team Stationary Point Count Surveys at Pagan, Marianas Archipelago, 2007
name: cred-rea-fish-team-stationary-point-count-surveys-at-pagan-marianas-archipelago-2007
notes: Stationary Point Counts at 4 stations at each survey site were surveyed as part of Rapid Ecological Assessments (REA) conducted at 9 sites around Pagan in the Marianas Archipelago (MA) during 25 May - 09 June 2007 in the NOAA Hi'ialakai (HI0703) Reef Assessment and Monitoring Program (RAMP) Cruise. Raw survey data included species level abundance estimates.
